{"tid":1217071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"十六號晚約咗朋友開party 準備以下物資","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:03:01.000Z","uid":14921,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0dac268214a189f2b783f59d0ca4aae49b40f56f","tid":1217071,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"同班朋友16號一齊去party 諗住玩吓輕量版war game<br />\n<br />\n咁同得朋友玩 緊係唔會用有傷害力 陣間俾人話咁點算呢<br />\n<br />\n我同朋友就諗咗以吓武具<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雞蛋</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPacUzt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPacUzt.png&h=a0d2e52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n整到對方臭 <br />\n整到眼部仲可能睇唔到嘢一陣<br />\n易攜<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n易爛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蕃茄</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OKASnf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OKASnf.png&h=e35882a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n整到對方臭<br />\n整到眼部仲可能睇唔到嘢一陣<br />\n易攜<br />\n相對雞蛋無咁易爛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">漆彈</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zu7CmiS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzu7CmiS.png&h=97cbf6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n受影響範圍大<br />\n整到眼部睇唔到嘢<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n制作需時<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家開party都可以帶呢啲嘢玩<br />\n當然再高level大家都可以準備<br />\n<br />\n一齊討論吓帶咩好玩"},{"pid":"be7517b242e1e9d66b8d3e8733644e64bdd3ea4e","tid":1217071,"uid":14921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"請大家準備好制造漆彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1214193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1214193</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n漆彈制作參考"},{"pid":"a9281c247b114a3163798010ff1f9aca4bca5f34","tid":1217071,"uid":73563,"li